products.name: Eternal Hopes
products.description:
240 GSM: High-quality, medium-weight fabric that offers durability and comfort.

100% Cotton Material: Made from pure cotton for a soft, breathable feel.

Pre-Shrunk: Ensures the garment retains its size and shape after washing.

Double Stitching: Reinforced stitching for added durability and longevity.

Super Combed Cotton: Enhanced softness and smoothness for maximum comfort.

No Colour Fading: Retains vibrant colors wash after wash.
